This paper deals with improving the performance of a multiple input single output (MISO) Gaussian broadcast channel through a novel user grouping precoder. The paper focuses on wireless communication systems and signal processing techniques, which are typically covered in the Information Theory (cs.IT), Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI), Signal Processing (cs.SI), Multimedia (cs.MM), and Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. However, since the paper does not explicitly mention machine learning, it is less likely to belong to the cs.LG sub-category.
